"""
SIMP Broker: Central Message Router

Acts as the central hub for inter-agent communication.
Receives intents, routes to appropriate agents, collects responses.

Security hardening (v0.2):
  - Thread-safe agent registry with separated secrets storage     (#3, #7)
  - Mandatory cryptographic signature verification                 (#2)
  - IP/endpoint obfuscation in all log messages                   (#14)
  - TTL-based intent record cleanup (background thread)           (#15)
  - Persistent SQLite audit logging                               (#16)
  - Distributed tracing via correlation_id / trace_id             (#17)
  - Periodic agent health checks with auto-deregistration         (#18)
  - Config-driven settings (env vars / config module)             (#19)
"""

